Add feature to save and load tasks in a hard disk.
commitResults.messageBody:
TaskList reloads when chatbot restarts.

This prevents users from keeping track of their task history.

Saving the tasks in a hard disk automatically whenever the task list
changes and loading the data from the hard disk when the chatbot starts
up allows users to better keep track of their task history.

Incorporate assertions into code
commitResults.messageBody:
There are no assertions in the code. There are only exceptions and
try-catch blocks.

Using assertions help to document important assumptions that should
hold at various points in the code. This helps in debugging.

Let's incorporate assertions in our code to make debugging easier.
